Package: opencpu
Type: Package
Title: OpenCPU framework for embedded statistics and reproducible research.
Version: 0.8
Date: 2013-07-27
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
License: Apache License (== 2.0)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: parallel, tools, stats, evaluate, RJSONIO, knitr, devtools, httr, brew, httpuv (>= 1.0.6.99), pander
Suggests: RAppArmor
SystemRequirements: pandoc, texlive, apparmor
Description: The OpenCPU framework exposes a clean HTTP API for interfacing R, Latex and Pandoc.
  It is available both as a single user server that runs in R, or as a cloud server that builds on rApache.
